    <item>
      <title>Open Learning 2017</title>
      <link>/2017/04/10/open-learning-2017/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 10 Apr 2017 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      
      <guid>/2017/04/10/open-learning-2017/</guid>
      <description>

&lt;p&gt;Season 2 of a project, which was (and is) inspired by &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/una/personal-goals&#34;&gt;Una Kravets&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;In high school I had the epiphany that it is better to follow good teachers then good topics. Throughout my studies I tried to follow that maxim as good as possible, but forgot about it recently. This year I want to re-establish my principle once more.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;hr /&gt;

