      <guid>/2017/04/09/viscos/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;Work in Progress.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;viscos&lt;/em&gt; is my take at syncrhonising and coordinating the different efforts
to build R visualisation-tools for the conceptual
rainfall-runoff model COSERO.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I will more about the concept &lt;em&gt;soonish&lt;/em&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Until then, feel free to explore visCOS for yourself:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://danklotz.github.io/viscos/index.html&#34;&gt;documentation&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/danklotz/visCOS&#34;&gt;package&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
</description>
